Title: Allow filesystems in /var/lib/docker/ to be monitored
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1572964472
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0i1

This is an extension to werk 6630. We do not want to discover container
filesystems, but in some cases true Filesystems are indeed mounted under
/var/lib/docker/, in such case a manual check needs to be configured.